OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FWatch the Operation Mille arrests
OL,9,FThree people have been arrested for
OL,10,Fimmigration offences in a recent
OL,11,Foperation led by Avon and Somerset
OL,12,FPolice.
OL,14,FThe force was accompanied by Driver
OL,15,Fand Vehicle Standards Agency and
OL,16,FImmigration Enforcement, in Operation
OL,17,FMille on 31 March.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
