OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FITV West Country was provided with
OL,8,Fexclusive on-the-day access while
OL,9,Fpolice worked along the Somerset
OL,10,Fsection of the A303 to disrupt and
OL,11,Fcreate a hostile environment for
OL,12,Forganised crime groups.
OL,14,FLess than five minutes into the
OL,15,Foperation, a first target was
OL,16,Facquired. An uninsured van registered
OL,17,Fto a third party, with two Namibian
OL,18,Fmen inside who had both overstayed in
OL,19,Fthe UK. They were arrested and served
OL,20,Fwith immigration paperwork.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FLater that day, acting on a tip,
OL,8,Fpolice and immigration officers
OL,9,Farrived on mass to an industrial park.
OL,11,FAn Albanian man was discovered to be
OL,12,Fworking illegally in breach of his
OL,13,Fvisa conditions. He was arrested and
OL,14,Fplaced on immigration bail.
OL,16,FThe business owner was also served
OL,17,Fwith a Civil Penalty Referral Notice
OL,18,Fand further inquiries into liability
OL,19,Fwill now be made. The liable employer
OL,20,Fcould face a penalty of up to #60,000.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FPC Dan Lawson explained: "A lot of it
OL,8,Fis safeguarding as far as we're
OL,9,Fconcerned - trafficking offences and
OL,10,Fthings like that. Because quite often
OL,11,Fthey're forced into things through
OL,12,Fduress."
OL,14,FHe added: "Proactive policing is
OL,15,Fdefinitely the way to bring crime
OL,16,Fdown. Police forces don't get enough
OL,17,Fmoney to do what they need to do."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
