OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FThe East Somerset District targeted by
OL,8,Fthe exercise is the biggest in Avon
OL,9,Fand Somerset, but there is a
OL,10,Ffrustration that it is too often
OL,11,Fneglected in favour of more densely-
OL,12,Fpopulated areas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
