OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FAside from the arrests, the operation
OL,8,Fresulted in two unroadworthy vehicles
OL,9,Fseized, more than 20 vehicles stopped,
OL,10,Ffive traffic tickets issued, 12 DVSA
OL,11,Fprohibitions issued, two searches
OL,12,Fconducted, two potential fail-to-stop
OL,13,Fincidents resolved, and more than 10
OL,14,Findividuals given words of advice or
OL,15,Feducational interventions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
