FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FIn a statement released afterwards, PC
OL,8,FLawson said: "Operation Mille
OL,9,Fdelivered a strong and positive day of
OL,10,Faction. From removing unsafe vehicles
OL,11,Fand making key arrests, to supporting
OL,12,Fchecks aimed at identifying
OL,13,Fimmigration offences, exploitation,
OL,14,Fand potential human trafficking risks,
OL,15,Fthis was a great example of how much
OL,16,Fcan be achieved when all our partners
OL,17,Fwork together with a shared purpose of
OL,18,Fkeeping people safe."
OL,26,@zD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
