PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,FImmigration Enforcement Inspector Dean
OL,8,FMunday said: "We are coming down hard
OL,9,Fon immigration offending in our
OL,10,Fcommunities to uphold our laws and
OL,11,Fprotect vulnerable people.
OL,13,F"That is why illegal working
OL,14,Fenforcement action is at the highest
OL,15,Flevel in British history, and we have
OL,16,Framped up removals of those with no
OL,17,Fright to be here to the highest rate
OL,18,Fin nearly a decade.
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
