OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775833866
OL,3,CThree people arrested for immigration
OL,4,Coffences in East Somerset police
OL,5,Coperation
OL,7,F"This operation was an excellent
OL,8,Fexample of partnership working and I
OL,9,Fhope it sends a clear signal that
OL,10,Fthere is no hiding place from the
OL,11,Frules."
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
